window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After a romantic disappointment and an undeserved demotion, Scots village bobby Hamish Macbeth decides a week's holiday at the coastal village of Skag might be just the ticket. </p> <p>He's dead wrong, of course: the food is dire, and the man in the next room nags his wife so loudly and continuously that more than one person at the Friendly House bed-and-breakfast wishes him dead, though only Hamish is heard threatening him. </p> <p>When this chap's body is found floating in the river Skag, Hamish is the prime suspect. </p>"; 
